// Memories
// This is a Egbert Van Alstyne/Gus Kahn song from 1916.
// The piece is in 6/8, not sure if using a 4/4 (or 2/4) rhythm gives
//  the correct feel, but it's sort of fun :)

Tempo 92
Keysig F

Groove Metronome2-4
  z * 2

Groove SwingIntro
Begin Solo
 Voice Organ1
 Decresc mf pp 4
 Octave 5
 Harmony 3
 Articulate 99
 Begin Riff
   23f+;43c+;4.a;
   23d+;43a;4.f;
   23g;43a;4.b;
   2.c+;
 End
End

Cresc mp mf 4
1    F    
2    Dm   
3    Gm   
4    C7   

Set Verse 1    // counter used to set arpeggio voicing

Repeat
Groove Swing
Volume m

5    F    
6    G7   
7    C7   
8    F7   

Groove SwingPlus
Swell f 4

if eq $verse 2
  Arpeggio Voice Piano1
  Arpeggio Volume +30
endif

9    Bb   
10   F    C7   F    
11   C    /    G7   
12   C7   

Groove SwingSus
Swell mp 4

13   F    
14   G7   
15   C7   
16   F    

Groove SwingPlusSus
if eq $verse 2
  Arpeggio Voice Piano1
  Arpeggio Volume +30
endif

17   Bb   /    Bdim3 
18   F    /    D7   

Repeatending

19   G7   /    C7   
20   F    

Inc Verse

RepeatEnd

Groove SwingEnd
Drum-Snare Volume -40
Decresc p 2
Tempo *.8 2

21   G7   /    C7   
22   F    /    z!   


